      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# 4.0.0 (2024.11.18)\r\n\r\nBack from the dead\r\n\r\nThis is an immature work from many years ago. Thank you all for using it. I have been away from ob development for too long, and I am no longer familiar with the code. I hope this version does not bring too many bugs.\r\n\r\n1. Removed `node-fetch-native` dependency\r\n2. Added support for `![](<image>)` type parsing [#156](https://github.com/renmu123/obsidian-image-auto-upload-plugin/issues/156)\r\n3. Added alt support for markdown [#143](https://github.com/renmu123/obsidian-image-auto-upload-plugin/issues/143)\r\n4. No longer trigger upload when dragging with the ctrl key pressed [#147](https://github.com/renmu123/obsidian-image-auto-upload-plugin/issues/147)\r\n5. Changed plugin name to \"Image auto upload\"\r\n\r\nBy the way, if this project has been helpful to you, please consider sponsoring me for a cola. It will help maintain the project better.\r\nAfdian: [https://afdian.com/a/renmu123](https://afdian.com/a/renmu123)\r\nYou can also charge my Bilibili account: [https://space.bilibili.com/10995238](https://space.bilibili.com/10995238)",
